REAL-TIME USE CASES OF BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY
===========================================


1. Digital Payments and Money Transfer
--------------------------------------
Simple Idea:
Send money quickly without banks or middlemen.

Explanation:
- Blockchain allows peer-to-peer money transfer.
- No bank or intermediary is required.
- Transactions are completed within minutes.
- Works across countries.

Examples:
- Bitcoin
- USDT
- Blockchain-based payment systems

Why Useful:
- Fast transactions
- Low transaction cost
- Available 24/7


